item.title: Hello, It's just about time...
item.description: Hello this is my first post here on my newly created site. I mainly create this site for the sole purpose of personal branding and displaying my future projects and which it will also serve me as a portfolio. Eventually I will populate this site and do my best to document every piece of information I learned and perhaps, I will apply it in some kind of project or at least, to use it as a reminder.
